  "body": "Closes https://github.com/coder/internal/issues/921\n\nThe flake in the linked issue was caused by the startup script taking longer than 1 second in CI. The existing conditional, that the startup script duration was under a second, was incorrect; the correct conditional is that the metric exists with the `success` label set to `true`.",
